rresponds to the health tracker and health token&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     flip over the top card and start the discard pile, where players will place cards once they are played&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;That's all there is to it! There is a range of actions and outcomes with the cards, and once a single hero remains, the game is over. You can play with or without the hero cards. Have no mercy &amp;ndash; and Slay Your Friends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
